articles.author: Hugh Son
articles.title: AI is already impacting the labor market, starting with young tech workers, Goldman economist says - CNBC
articles.description: Unemployment rates among tech workers between 20 and 30 years old jumped by 3 percentage points since the start of this year, said Goldman Sachs' Joseph Briggs.
articles.content:
Changes to the American labor market brought on by the arrival of generative AI are already showing up in employment data, according to a Goldman Sachs economist.
